OL,6,FMr Justice Kerr said Mr Rickards had
OL,7,Fsuffered five stab wounds, including
OL,8,Ftwo through his heart, and it was
OL,9,Fclear that his wife had intended to
OL,10,Fkill him.
OL,12,FHis body is thought to have been
OL,13,Fstored in a cupboard in the flat and
OL,14,Flater moved to the garden.
OL,16,FThe judge said officers investigating
OL,17,Fher on suspicion of fraud for using
OL,18,Fhis bank card found the body in a
OL,19,Fholdall after being alerted by an
OL,20,F"overpowering odour" that "made them
OL,21,Ffeel ill".
