OL,6,FInsights into their turbulent 27-year
OL,7,Fmarriage became clear in video clips
OL,8,Ftaken by Rickards, which showed her
OL,9,Fabusing, beating and mocking her
OL,10,Fhusband.
OL,12,FWhen arrested, Maureen Rickards kept
OL,13,Fup the act, asking "what body?"
OL,15,FShe did not attend her final
OL,16,Fsentencing, but the judge directed his
OL,17,Fcomments towards her, saying: "You
OL,18,Ffilmed various incidents.
