OL,6,F"Your videos also clearly show you
OL,7,Fthreatening Jeremy, abusing him, using
OL,8,Fviolence on him, and expressing an
OL,9,Fintention to kill him. He was in frail
OL,10,Fhealth and largely defenceless against
OL,11,Fyou.
OL,13,F"Your voice can be heard in the
OL,14,Fbackground, threatening to kill him.
OL,16,F"He may have died on the ninth of
OL,17,FJune, the date you later told your
OL,18,Fdaughter he had died.
