OL,6,F"If it was not on the ninth of June,
OL,7,Fit was shortly after that he was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death in the attic room.
OL,10,F"He received five stab wounds, two of
OL,11,Fwhich pierced his heart.
OL,13,F"I am sure you intended his death and
OL,14,Fnothing less.
OL,16,F"The wounds could not have been
OL,17,Finflicted by someone intending only
OL,18,Freally serious harm.
OL,20,F"You hid his body in the attic room
OL,21,Fcupboard, probably for some days."
