OL,6,FThe judge said he was "sure" that when
OL,7,FRickards used her husband's bank card
OL,8,Fto buy cleaning products, it was to
OL,9,Ftry to get rid of blood from the
OL,10,Fcarpet in the cupboard.
OL,12,FGardeners had visited the property on
OL,13,FJune 26 and Rickards asked them to
OL,14,F"leave the grass they had cut under
OL,15,Fsome bushes", the court had heard.
OL,17,FMr Rickards' body was later found in
OL,18,Fthat location.
