OL,6,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,7,FInspector Colin McKeen said: "Maureen
OL,8,FRickards carried out the vicious
OL,9,Fmurder of her husband Jeremy before
OL,10,Fattempting to hide his body in their
OL,11,Fgarden.
OL,13,F"She then sought to frustrate the
OL,14,Finvestigation and has repeatedly
OL,15,Frefused to admit what she did, forcing
OL,16,Fa trial at which a jury saw through
OL,17,Fher deception. She will now serve many
OL,18,Fyears in prison.
